#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"This is the documentation for YunoHost,<br/>\n"
"an **operating system** aiming to **simplify server administration**!\n"
msgstr ""
"Esta é a documentación para YunoHost,<br/>\n"
"un **sistema operativo** co obxectivo de **simplificar a administración dun servidor**!\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "If you are an **impatient power user**, you may want to try YunoHost, or jump right away to install:\n"
msgstr "Se es **unha usuaria con experiencia e pouca paciencia**, podes primeiro probar YunoHost, ou ir directamente á instalación:\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<Button url=\"/admin/what_is_yunohost\">🤔 What's YunoHost?!</Button>\n"
"<Button url=\"/admin/what_is_yunohost/demo\">⚗️ Try YunoHost</Button>\n"
"<Button url=\"/admin/get_started/install_on\">🚀 Install</Button>\n"
msgstr ""
"<Button url=\"/admin/what_is_yunohost\">🤔 Que é YunoHost?!</Button>\n"
"<Button url=\"/admin/what_is_yunohost/demo\">⚗️ Probar YunoHost</Button>\n"
"<Button url=\"/admin/get_started/install_on\">🚀 Instalar</Button>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "<Button url=\"https://apps.yunohost.org/\">📦 Browse the app catalog</Button>\n"
msgstr "<Button url=\"https://apps.yunohost.org/\">📦 Olla o catálogo de aplicacións</Button>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "Are you **new to self-hosting and servers in general**? We recommend taking it slow and go through the pages presenting [self-hosting](/admin/about_self_hosting), the [different modes](/admin/get_started/methods) and [other](/admin/get_started/why_should_you_not_host_yourself) [things](/category/providers) you should know prior to jumping into the action!\n"
msgstr "**Non tes experiencia** no eido da auto-hospedaxe e servidores en xeral? Recomendámosche que o tomes con calma e leas as páxinas relativas á [auto-hospedaxe](/admin/about_self_hosting), os [diversos xeitos de conseguilo](/admin/get_started/methods) e [outros asuntos](/admin/get_started/why_should_you_not_host_yourself) [things](/category/providers) que deberías coñecer antes de lanzarte de cabeza!\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "Are you **already using YunoHost**? You may want to get in touch with the community or reach for help:\n"
msgstr "Xa **utilizas YunoHost**? Pode interesarche relacionarte coa comunidade ou pedir axuda:\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<Button url=\"https://forum.yunohost.org\">📢 Forum</Button>\n"
"<Button url=\"/community/chat_rooms\">🗫  Chat rooms</Button>\n"
"<Button url=\"/community/help\">🛟 Help</Button>\n"
msgstr ""
"<Button url=\"https://forum.yunohost.org\">📢 Foro</Button>\n"
"<Button url=\"/community/chat_rooms\">🗫  Salas de conversa</Button>\n"
"<Button url=\"/community/help\">🛟 Axuda</Button>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "Finally, you can **support the project** or get involved in [different ways](/dev):\n"
msgstr "Finalmente, podes **apoiar o proxecto** ou involucrarte de [varias formas](/dev):\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<Button url=\"https://yunohost.org/donate.html\">💰 Donate</Button>\n"
"<Button url=\"/dev/doc\">📝 Improve the documentation</Button>\n"
"<Button url=\"/dev/doc\">🌐 Work on translations</Button>\n"
"<Button url=\"/dev/packaging\">📦 Learn app packaging</Button>\n"
"<Button url=\"/dev/core\">⚙️  Develop on the core</Button>\n"
msgstr ""
"<Button url=\"https://yunohost.org/donate.html\">💰 Doar</Button>\n"
"<Button url=\"/dev/doc\">📝 Mellorar a documentación</Button>\n"
"<Button url=\"/dev/doc\">🌐 Traballar na tradución</Button>\n"
"<Button url=\"/dev/packaging\">📦 Aprender a empaquetar aplicacións</Button>\n"
"<Button url=\"/dev/core\">⚙️  Desenvolvemento do núcleo</Button>\n"

